                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/11812: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hankow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-12-27T10:00:00+08:00"
                            >December 27, 1937—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received December 27—1:35 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>107. Was informed last night that German Ambassador presented Generalissimo
                    yesterday with a note conveying terms understood to be very drastic from
                    Japanese military. I understand terms will be published by Foreign Office today
                    or tomorrow.</p>
                <p>Sent to Shanghai. Shanghai please repeat to Tokyo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
